    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable transportation with strong value for the money. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer looking for a low-cost option, a project, or a practical spare car. Offered as an honest, budget-conscious choice with plenty of potential for the right owner. Priced to sell and ready for its next chapter.",
