      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts up, gets you where you need to go, and could be a great fit for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s got the usual wear you\u2019d expect for its age, but at this price there\u2019s real value here. If you want something budget-friendly without the fuss, come have a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project with strong enthusiast potential. The drivetrain pulls through the revs, steering feels direct, and it presents as a usable platform for a commuter, shop truck, or weekend build. Cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections are present, but that also means you can drive it, sort it, and improve it without worrying about keeping a trailer queen pristine. A good candidate for someone who appreciates mechanical simplicity, easy service access, and the chance to put their own touch on a capable chassis.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way to get from A to B. Used, rough, and priced right. Great fixer or budget daily. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with the kind of presence that still turns heads, this car has the unmistakable charm of a machine that\u2019s lived a full life and still has more stories to tell. It\u2019s the sort of ride that speaks to the optimist, the tinkerer, or anyone looking for an affordable entry into something with real personality. Whether you\u2019re after a weekend project, a budget runabout, or a platform to make your own, this one offers plenty of character and possibility at a price that leaves room to dream.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
